  <h1 class="gd-h1">Weather and Down-Days in Heliskiing</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Every prospective heliskier worries about the same thing: what if the weather closes in and I lose days to the sky? It is a fair concern, and an honest one deserves an honest answer. Below is a clear guide to why heliskiing is weather-dependent, what a good operator does about it, and how the way the sport is sold protects you, before you look at <a href="/packages">the packages</a> or the detail on <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
